---
title: Double Sri Lankan Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Mayonnaise & Flaked Almonds
description: We give you the aromatic scents of a Sri Lankan inspired spice mix , tender chicken and a warm palette of crispy roast veggies. Combine them together to enrich your dinner with colour and flavour. You won’t be disappointed in how everything tastes so undeniably good.

*We’ve replaced the potato in this recipe with cauliflower due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
